I went and looked back over my assignment #1 and found that "Creately"
was the best (free) UML dagramming program that I could find.
They have an online version and it's easy enough to use.
Mostly drag-and-drop and the end product looks clean.

Here is a link for creating Use Case Diagrams online:
https://creately.com/diagram-type/use-case

